# ── axcore-v1 runtime (when fe-compiler is run locally) ──────────────────────
.axcore_runtime/
.artifacts/
.claude/worktrees/

# ── Generated install / runtime state (NEVER source-of-truth) ────────────────
# `fe-compiler-v1` is a source-only compiler/plugin package. It must
# never accumulate Spec Kit install state or runtime SKILLs — those
# belong in the runtime home (`idea-engine`). If `.specify/` or
# `.claude/skills/` ever appear here, they are accidental and ignored.
# Authored `.claude/CLAUDE.md` STAYS tracked — only `skills/` is ignored.
.specify/
.claude/skills/

# Per-user local Claude Code permissions / project state. Local-only.
.claude/settings.local.json

# ── Wrong-runtime-home regression dirs (legacy / accidental) ─────────────────
.runs/
.compiler_runtime/
